summary: This document is an email chain from July 19, 2021, regarding a subpoena request for a birth certificate from the Massachusetts Registry of Vital Records and Statistics. The request is made by an FBI Special Agent from the New York Field Office's Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force, concerning an individual identified as 'ML'.

persons.name: Special Agent
persons.context: The FBI Special Agent from the New York Field Office's Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force is requesting a subpoena for a birth certificate for an individual identified as 'ML'.

events.title: Subpoena Request for Birth Certificate
events.description: An FBI Special Agent requests a subpoena to obtain a birth certificate for an individual identified as 'ML' from the Massachusetts Registry of Vital Records and Statistics.

locations: Registry of Vital Records and Statistics, 150 Mt. Vernon Street, 1st Floor, Dorchester, MA 02125
keyFacts: The FBI was actively investigating an individual identified as 'ML' as of July 2021, seeking their birth certificate from Massachusetts.
The investigation was handled by the Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force at the FBI's New York Field Office.
The document shows standard investigative procedure (subpoena request) being followed to obtain official records.
